---
title: Chicken Piccata & Roasted Veggies with Parsley Butter Sauce
description: This may sound fancy, but that’s just because we’ve taken inspiration from Italy. This kid-approved combo of flavoursome chicken steaks, roasted veggies and a smooth buttery sauce ticks all the boxes for a tasty and wholesome dinner.

*Unfortunately, this week's courgette was in short supply, so we've replaced it with parsnip. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-piccata-26701edd.jpg
